{"tid":2006832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梓樂離世半年 科大今辦追悼會","createTime":"2020-05-08T04:50:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T05:08:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c9ea13a44010f2e1ac55c5da7b9631c64991e536","tid":2006832,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:50:11.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200508/QNK47BAJEAVRGMPNRXSLELSSTM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200508%2FQNK47BAJEAVRGMPNRXSLELSSTM%2F&d=kJsi%2B77Adq7yP7dZlTZe0BjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=ee9bd75b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200508%2FQNK47BAJEAVRGMPNRXSLELSSTM%2F&h=8950aea3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200508/QNK47BAJEAVRGMPNRXSLELSSTM/</a><br />\n<br />\n梓樂離世半年 科大今辦追悼會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200508/large/1588868914_e656.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200508%2Flarge%2F1588868914_e656.gif&h=109d3844&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n科大生周梓樂離世半年，科大學生會今日將舉行悼念活動。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】科技大學學生周梓樂去年11月離奇墮樓，今日是離世半年，科大學生會今晚在校內舉行「周同學逝世半年追悼會」。科大學生會表示，有信心大家未遺忘梓樂，希望藉着梓樂逝世半年的悼念活動，提醒香港人半年前曾發生一件沉冤待雪的大事，「希望大家諗返起個初心。」<br />\n<br />\n分組獻花防犯聚<br />\n<br />\n科大學生會今晚6時在校內賽馬會大樓（Atrium）設祭壇舉辦追悼會。科大學生會外務副會長朱凱琳表示，校方已知悉。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n她指參加者會分批獻白花及燃點白蠟燭；同時為響應全港各區白絲帶悼念行動，學生會會準。。。。。。。。。她呼籲全港市民今晚8時9分一同為梓樂默哀1分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n她又指，科大去年反送中運動期間，已限制只供科大成員進入，公眾人士如入內須提早一日登記。學。。。。。。。。。。。。決定追悼會只供科大師生、持有效校友證件的校友參加，傳媒如入內採訪亦須事先登記。她解釋，故意提早在傍晚開始追。。。。。。。。。。。。回。」<br />\n<br />\n■記者周 婷"},{"pid":"54e6def6876eb88afd9d6bc67e9a300c6307ac32","tid":2006832,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:51:20.000Z","msg":"。。。。。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4bbdf6837222c06c094d6039025676bdd89c356","tid":2006832,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T04:58:04.000Z","msg":"黑警會唔會又去踩場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c4b7ba3a7d20c0792bd745ac62d50f197af036","tid":2006832,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T05:05:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c79026a9a4d0454f54620fc35a80d18521d5d48d","tid":2006832,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T05:07:41.000Z","msg":"屎維：香港再出發<br />\n周梓樂wfc"},{"pid":"b43ede4793cbcc2b1931ccf72bfcabfe04b06bb0","tid":2006832,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T05:08:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c728c5b09ea28a446d0fe3a935fbc859560d5945","tid":2006832,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T05:08:49.000Z","msg":"黑警又會出動「幫手」了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}